(3, 93, 51, 0, '', '', '', '', '', 'Exploring quantum dynamics via ergodic properties of expectation values of observables.Random walks on heirarchical graphs and fractals. Recurrence-statistics in coarse gradined dynamical systems.', '1', '3', '2022-03-17 12:15:51'),
